gem install syntaxi
gem install sqlite3-ruby (if you don't have it)

An idea from Mike@AI - allow coding issues to surface through a chat like interface and reward help. Currently programs like Slack solve this issue, however they do not have the rewarding aspect.

Originally hosted on Google code here <a href="https://code.google.com/p/bubbles/">https://code.google.com/p/bubbles/</a> and moved because they are shutting down.
